      m_Calls: []
  m_text: <b>Gandalf</b> is the grey pilgrim, a wanderer of hidden roads and quiet
    counsel. He walks the edge between shadow and hope, guiding the small and the
    humble because he knows their courage can outlast any sword.He trusts in patience,
    in wisdom earned by travel, and in the spark that lights when others have given
    in to fear.<br><br>The Shire lies under his watch, and the first steps of his
    journey begin among its green lanes, where he gathers trusted companions, listens
    for the first uneasy rumors, and searches old ground for relics that have waited
    too long. His path starts in quiet places, but it will not remain quiet.
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 1ea3c05212e47c140a3c622b0f5f07f0, type: 2}
