    Istari, master of lore, ring-craft, and the long devices of the Wise. His voice
    is a weapon finer than steel, entering the counsels of kings and bending proud
    hearts with honeyed reason until obedience seems wisdom and surrender seems peace.<br><br>This
    variant favors influence, manipulation, and command exercised with polished restraint.
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
